name: Space Mouse One HEN #1
description: The "Space Mouse One" characters are based on the comic series by Cinetube "Of Austronauts and Mice" (to be published). The works are handmade and not produced automatically!. The drawings, collages, digital treatments, are inspired by street art, artists like Banksy, cryptoart, social and cultural trends. This is a special edition to be published on HEN
